title: Miami Supercops
description:
Starring: William Jim, C.V. Wood, Terence Hill, Jackie Castellano, C.B. Seay, Richard Liberty, Rhonda S. Lundstead, Ken Ceresne, Bud Spencer
Directed by: Bruno CorbucciIn Miami Supercops, Terence Hill and Bud Spencer are two courageous crimefighters on the trail of $20 million, stolen in a heist some years before. It?s murder, mayhem and pandemonium all the way as they track down the money - and their man - with, of course, a little help from two beautiful girls!
